The projection is then called as:
http://localhost:8080/api/cities/1?projection=CityProjection

findByNameAndCountryAllIgnoringCase:
http://localhost:8080/api/cities/search/findByNameAndCountryAllIgnoringCase?name=Melbourne&country=Australia

findByNameContainingAndCountryContainingAllIgnoringCase:
http://localhost:8080/api/cities/search/findByNameContainingAndCountryContainingAllIgnoringCase?name=&country=UK


